                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-1322" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH BIGNELL</persName>
                  </hi>. My husband is a butler; I live in Blackland-street, Chelsea. In January, this year, I paid the prisoner 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. on Mr. Goodwin's account—this is the receipt I took for it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400817-name-1323" type="witnessName">
