                        <interp inst="t18400817-name-1323" type="given" value="ABRAHAM"></interp>ABRAHAM GOBBETT</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Green-street, Marlborough-road, Chel<lb></lb>sea. In May, this year, I paid the prisoner 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for Mr. Goodwin, and took this receipt for it, which the prisoner wrote.</p>
